                    <p className="text-gray-300 mb-6 max-w-md">感谢您的预约，我们的团队将尽快通过 WhatsApp 联系您确认席位。</p>
                    <div className="p-4 bg-white/5 rounded border border-white/10 text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8">
